
USAGE: banish <site/name>

This command will banish either a certain player, or
in extreme cases a whole site.

banish zifnab

This would mean that Zifnab could no longer log onto the mud

banish 129.188.147.100

This would prevent anyone form that particular site to log onto the mud


*****  NOTES

This also can be achieved through the admin tool.
Type admtool and choose option b from the menu.


